{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"84e177ee14","title":"中共中央转发贵州省委关于一九六O年秋粮分配征购工作指示的批示","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6e301ceb4b","index":0,"year":1960,"month":9,"day":2,"articleId":"84e177ee14"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fa47521b63","type":"title","text":"中共中央转发贵州省委关于一九六O年秋粮分配征购工作指示的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"84e177ee14"},{"id":"39e78629bc","type":"appellation","text":"各省、市、自治区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"84e177ee14"},{"id":"388400c965","type":"paragraph","text":"贵州省委关于一九六O年秋粮分配征购工作的指示很好，现转发各地参考。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"84e177ee14"},{"id":"636a05306a","type":"paragraph","text":"贵州省委对于农村口粮的安排，是符合北戴河工作会议的精神的。总之，应当把十二个月的粮食匀做十三个月安排，留一个月的准备粮。这样，留有余地，工作就更加主动。现在农村食堂化了，我们具体负责五亿多农民的吃饭问题，没有一点准备粮是不行的。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"84e177ee14"},{"id":"7a5d9ea728","type":"paragraph","text":"农村人民公社办的企业、事业人员的口粮还是像贵州省委规定的那样，按农村口粮标准安排为好。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"84e177ee14"},{"id":"55806f77a7","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央一九六O年九月二日","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"84e177ee14"}],"page":{"id":"baba59022b","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"84e177ee14","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}